13 no firearm was surrendered, be required to produce within thirty days said license to carry
14 firearms, firearm identification card, or receipt for fee paid for such card, failing which the
15 conditions of section one hundred and twenty-nine D will apply. Nothing in this section shall
16 prevent any person from being prosecuted for any violation of this chapter."
